\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af8\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f5
Ochranu mlad\u253\'fdch \u318\'3eud\u237\'ed pred negat\u237\'edvnymi vplyvmi m\u233\'e9di\u237\'ed na\u353\'61e z\u225\'e1kony rie\u353\'61ia. Prax v\u353\'61ak uk\u225\'e1zala, \u382\'7ee v pr\u225\'e1vnych predpisoch nie je vyrie\u353\'61en\u253\'fd z\u225\'e1kaz vysiela\u357\'65 v \u269\'0dase, ke\u271\'0f telev\u237\'edzie masovo sleduj\u250\'fa aj deti a dospievaj\u250\'faca gener\u225\'e1cia up\u250\'fatavky na ve\u269\'0dern\u233\'e9, v s\u250\'falade so z\u225\'e1konom vysielan\u233\'e9 rel\u225\'e1cie obsahuj\u250\'face sc\u233\'e9ny re\u225\'e1lneho n\u225\'e1silia. V navrhovanej novele z\u225\'e1kona teda chceme t\u250\'fato medzeru v pr\u225\'e1vnych predpisoch odstr\u225\'e1ni\u357\'65.}
\par \pard\plain \s0\ql\widctlpar\faauto\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi0\ltrpar{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\dbch\af7\afs24\alang1025\cf0\kerning1\langfe2052\dbch\af8\loch\f0\fs24\lang1051\qj\li0\ri0\lin0\rin0\fi709{\afs30\rtlch \ltrch\loch\fs30\loch\f5
